# File: grunt backup/vendor.js.ab
# Purpose: Backup copy of the vendor JavaScript bundle from an earlier Grunt build snapshot
# Dependencies: [vendor.js.ab]

## Overview
A preserved copy of a vendor.js build artifact stored in the `grunt backup/` directory. Contains the same types of content as the root `vendor.js` — all Bower-managed vendor JavaScript libraries concatenated and minified. Approximately 980 KB, slightly smaller than the `build files - backup/` copy, indicating a different build iteration with potentially fewer or older library versions.

## Interface
No exports. A reference/archive file not loaded by the running application.

## Dependencies
- vendor.js.ab — the canonical source this was copied from

## Implementation Notes
- File size: ~980 KB
- Part of the `grunt backup/` directory snapshot, captured at a different time than `build files - backup/vendor.js`
- Not referenced by any active build configuration or `app/index.html`
